headline: How the Narrative Around Lululemon Is Shifting Amid New Challenges and Analyst Caution
summary: Lululemon athletica's fair value target has slipped to $193.54 from $194.36, reflecting recently updated analyst projections as sentiment shifts around the company. The slight dip comes as expectations evolve due to ongoing management changes and challenges in North American demand.
